This script utilizes **SLURM** (Simple Linux Utility for Resource Management) to manage the execution of a Python script named **train.py**. The script performs a training task using the **ResNet50V2** model on the **ISIC2019** database with an image size of **150x150 pixels**. It utilizes a **conda environment** named "clean_chimera_env" for dependency management.
